data.name: Artifice.LTD's ArtSynth2
data.describe: Type "go" to generate an image based on two randomly selected artists' styles. Type "again" to generate another image in the same style (or type in the style ID to return to a previously created style). You may append "horizontal, vertical, or square" to generate a new image in a specific format.
data.author: Shawn T Adams

ai_content.synopsis: ArtSynth2 on ChatGPT is a web application developed by Artifice.LTD. It allows users to generate images based on the styles of two randomly selected artists. Users can also generate more images in the same style or return to a previously created style by inputting the style ID. Additionally, users have the option to generate images in specific formats such as horizontal, vertical, or square.
